title: House of the Dragon S1: Episode 7 Preview
description:
Join us for a spoiler-filled discussion of House of the Dragon, looking at episode 5 and looking forward to episode 7, with guest Jason Concepcion of the official House of the Dragon Podcast and X-Ray Vision Pod!

Jason Concepcion: https://linktr.ee/jason_concepcion
